stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle
    idle --> loading : START
    loading --> loading : R1 / R2 / R3 / R4 / R5\n(sections révélées progressivement)
    loading --> complete : COMPLETE
    loading --> error : ERROR (fatal)
    loading --> loading : error_r3 / error_r4\n(dégradation gracieuse)
    complete --> idle : RESET
    error --> idle : RESET
